<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I don't care what anone says this axe isn't all that its cracked up to be. The stats r avergae and 3str well I buff for 15str and nothing with the dmg changes but the fact that this is sold for 200pp+ is laughable. The axe of the iron back which stats r 16dmg 37delay is sold for less. Just wanna say do not waste ur time or pp in getting this weapon.</font></td></tr></table>
